com.petpet.c3po.adaptor.fits
Class DigesterContext

java.lang.Object
  com.petpet.c3po.adaptor.fits.DigesterContext

public class DigesterContext
extends Object

The digester context is a simple helper object that is pushed onto the Apache Digester stack and its methods are used during SAX parsing.

Author:
Petar Petrov
